        "html": "=<p>A substitution has been applied.</p><p><strong>Meeting Instance ID:</strong> {{ $('Parse Attendance').item.json.meetingInstanceId }}<br><strong>Original Attendance ID:</strong> {{ $('Parse Attendance').item.json.attendanceId }}<br><strong>Substitute:</strong> {{ $('Build Sub Calendar Patch').item.json.subName }} ({{ $('Build Sub Calendar Patch').item.json.subEmail }})</p><p>The calendar occurrence has been updated with the substitute's information.</p>",
